description: This header file defines a mock class for the SecureStorageService gRPC service, using Google Mock framework. The class inherits from the service's base class and mocks its methods, enabling unit testing of components that depend on this service.

classes.name: SecureStorageServiceMock
classes.description: A mock class for the SecureStorageService gRPC service, allowing unit tests to simulate and verify interactions with the service.

methods.name: GetValue
methods.description: Mock method for retrieving a value from secure storage via gRPC.

methods.name: UpdateValue
methods.description: Mock method for updating a value in secure storage via gRPC.

methods.name: DeleteValue
methods.description: Mock method for deleting a specific value in secure storage via gRPC.

methods.name: DeleteAllValues
methods.description: Mock method for deleting all values in secure storage via gRPC.

methods.name: SeedValue
methods.description: Mock method for seeding secure storage with initial data via gRPC.
